00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,320
And

600
00:19:05,320 --> 00:19:07,200
if you think it's really delicious,

601
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,120
when you get to the city,

602
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:09,520
give me some publicity.

603
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:10,380
You can do that.

604
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:11,800
I'll eat first.

605
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:12,360
Delicious.

606
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:13,320
I'll promote it for you.

607
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:14,120
It must be delicious.

608
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,000
If not,

609
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,080
you'll ruin my reputation.

610
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:16,440
Okay.

611
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,370
Let's eat, guys.

612
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,120
This meal is on me.

613
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:20,320
Don't take it from me.

614
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:21,640
Go to the ball.

615
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:24,560
A little hand that brings wealth.
